ing: 2 (8 ounce) packages fresh mozzarella cheese marinated in olive oil
des: "These appetizers are so delicious and I have received so many compliments on them!"
ins: Place a slice of prosciutto on a work surface; top with 1 basil leaf and 1 mozzarella ball. Roll prosciutto around basil and mozzarella cheese and secure with a toothpick. Repeat process, alternating with soppressata, until all ingredients are used. Refrigerate until serving.
